data.value: Starting at the check digit, every other digit to the left should be multiplied by 2 If there are double-digit numbers, add the digits together [2, 4, 6, 8] => [4, 8, 12, 16] => [9, 3, 3, 7] = 22 Sum all of the digits, and add it to the total; if it is divisible by 10, it's valid [1, 3, 5, 7, 2] + 22 => 18 + 22 = 40 40 Mod 10 = 0 (therefore it's valid)
